title: Unlock the biggest secrets of SuperCoach NRL for FREE
text:
>> START YOUR SUPERCOACH DIPLOMA HERE << 
Whether you consider yourself a SuperCoach NRL gun, semi-gun or just a battler, you can become a “qualified” SuperCoach NRL SuperCoach today! Complete your Diploma here online , just like any other course within the OTEN TAFE NSW curriculum. 
The Diploma consists of four units and quizzes, takes about 15 minutes and when you’ve passed you’ll get your very own diploma, signed by Roosters legend Anthony Minicheillo and our resident expert Tom Sangster. 
Print it out, put it on the wall, post it to social media and rub it in to your mates. 
To get your diploma, simply: 
• Register here — with OTEN TAFE NSW using your SuperCoach NRL email address and any password you nominate. 
• Watch — Four educational videos and complete a few multiple choice questions for all four units. 
• Wait — to receive your SuperCoach NRL Diploma via email (so make sure you use your SuperCoach NRL email address) and a SuperCoach Diploma badge in the game. 
IMPORTANT: If you have any questions about the Diploma, ask them on our SuperCoach NRL Central community page on Facebook. 
>> START YOUR SUPERCOACH DIPLOMA HERE << How your Diploma will look FRAMED and the SuperCoach NRL badge you will receive Source: The Daily Telegraph 
*The SuperCoach NRL Diploma is not an accredited TAFE NSW qualification. It is however excellent to post to our Facebook community page with the hashtag #LiftYourGame Sign up for Sportsmail
